text: The Cowboy and The Countess is a 1926 American western movie. It was directed by Roy William Neill. Actors include Buck Jones, Helena D'Algy, Diana Miller, Harvey Clark, and Monte Collins. It was distributed by 20th Century Fox. ==Other websites== * Category:1926 movies Category:1920s Western (genre) movies Category:American Western (genre) movies Category:American silent movies Category:Movies directed by Roy William Neill
